Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:12.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:30.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:43.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:27.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:33.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:37.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:49.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:55.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.49,0:22:57.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:08.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:16.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:22.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:27.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:32.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:38.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.11,0:23:44.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:48.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:52.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:56.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}远方的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次出现在中央都市的斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德和阿尔为了把人造人拽出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和麟合作故意引出斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人库拉多尼和拉斯出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用苦无挡开了正面斩击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作要快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰芳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为能从我的眼中逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来很习惯战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直向我左眼侧方的死角移动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的话 谁也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来问些问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道库拉多尼肚子里的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把那个累赘扔了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人也许还能逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说是累赘？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这个国家最伟大的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得是 金格·布拉德雷大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王是为了人民而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人民就不存在王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法成为真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳臭未干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上不存在真正的王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太依赖眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从风的流向来看 出口在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的眼睛还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以做个好孩子 好好看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也许把休斯先生的背影当成了父亲的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔来看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人很怕寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克蕾西亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克兄弟又在闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都是宪兵跑来跑去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又打架？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手好像是一直瞄准国家炼金术师的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没抓住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 为什么会重叠到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪许可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟的信号弹还没发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还是争取点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明也在使用炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么将炼金术师作为叛逆神灵的人而极端厌恶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在东方之都也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你们制造的人就有我这样破坏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是借用神的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让杀人正当化罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修·塔克和妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是被你借用神的执行者的名义杀死的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你们也看过那个合成兽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造出那种东西的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们所崇拜的炼金术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你那双手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把弟弟的身体变得无药可救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能产生什么的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是这种自负才产生了那只合成兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要杀死她？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么夺走了她的生命？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不早就明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只合成兽再也变不回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果弃之不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被作为实验动物来对待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一生都无法再作为人来被对待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我们心里隐约感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许妮娜会就这么被作为实验动物而送走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把怎么都无法解决的问题放到了一边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 我们炼金术师一直在犯各种错误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法承认你所做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否还记得姓洛克贝尔的亚美斯多利斯人医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶赴内乱的伊修瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在歼灭战的命令下达之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一直给伊修瓦尔人治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:10:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否记得救了你却被你杀死的医生夫妇？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人杀了爸爸和妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被自己救的人杀了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们根本没有做什么该被杀的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把爸爸和妈妈还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你仇恨的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是复仇只会萌生新一轮的复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个医生的女儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有杀我的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长 国军已经来到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种研究放到一边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个纹身是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术的基础是 理解 分解 再构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个右臂是分解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂是再构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究东方的炼丹术之后 我自己改良的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个基础上明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的炼金术很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 国军…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你兄长的研究也许能拯救伊修瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为兵器 用惊人的力量蹂躏伊修瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明同样是亚美斯多利斯的国民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个和兄长的研究有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能找出和国家炼金术师对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至超越他们的强大力量 来歼灭军队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用超越力量的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用炼金术报复他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血债要血偿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是兄长所热衷的炼金术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使兄长是为了人民 为了幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谁也不会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是炼金术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西能拯救伊修瓦尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是重复破坏和杀戮的这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早就做好了逃跑的准备是不幸中的万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我整理了重要的东西 所以迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 你拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的研究书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能拿出这一本了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着这个逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么好的研究就全没了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己拿着逃就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是积累了严格修行的武僧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 你活下来的几率更高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 我两脚的颤抖停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个没用的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国军的士兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成阵 是国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 止不住血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂 弟弟的手臂在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去 不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们瞧瞧伊修瓦尔的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更应该逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我不是为了让你去送死才救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生才是 应该和夫人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,患者不要担心别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 居然护着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自力逃跑的人就赶紧逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动 伤口会裂开的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 过来 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁来用那边的板车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他也一起带走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静剂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有了 剩下的全部用在刚才的男孩身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美斯多利斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些混蛋 这些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克贝尔医生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能拿着那东西 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 开枪的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将把你视作敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋 你要是向温莉出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:19:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就杀了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须有一边倒下 否则仇恨的连锁无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个内乱首先扣下扳机的 是亚美斯多利斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点放下枪离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没法开枪的话 就离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋哥哥 在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想两个人一起死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把温莉带到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉 把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他杀了爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想杀了爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在拉修巴雷给婴儿接生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救了母子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给了我能够再次站起来的手和脚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手不是杀人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是救人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护就必须舍弃什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有牺牲觉悟的人就会失去并倒地不起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 守护的觉悟会传播
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凌驾于灾厄之上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,0:24:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.02,0:24:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第23话 战场的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.15,0:24:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤的泪水不会轻易示人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是约定
